StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [UpdateQSNRSS]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
(@strQSNID char(9) ,@AssignedRSS int ,@UserLogin varchar(50)) AS
IF EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM QSN WHERE QSN_ID = @strQSNID) BEGIN UPDATE QSN SET AssignedRssOrgId = @AssignedRSS, USER_LOGIN = @UserLogin WHERE QSN_ID = @strQSNID
END
